{\kerning0\rtlch\ab0\ltrch\hich\af7\alang2057\ab0\dbch\ab0\loch\f7\lang2057\b0\par}\pard\plain \s0\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\faauto\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang7177\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang7177\dbch\af8\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang7177\widctlpar\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\kerning0\f7\lang2057
Tuy\u234\'ean b\u7889\'3f gi\u7845\'3fy ph\u233\'e9p n\u224\'e0y c\u7845\'3fu th\u224\'e0nh m\u7897\'3ft th\u7887\'3fa thu\u7853\'3fn ph\u225\'e1p l\u253\'fd gi\u7919\'3fa b\u7841\'3fn (v\u7899\'3fi t\u432\'3f c\u225\'e1ch c\u225\'e1 nh\u226\'e2n ho\u7863\'3fc m\u7897\'3ft t\u7893\'3f ch\u7913\'3fc \u273\'3f\u417\'3fn l\u7867\'3f) v\u224\'e0 C\u225\'e1c Nh\u224\'e0 Cung C\u7845\'3fp cho s\u7843\'3fn ph\u7849\'3fm ph\u7847\'3fn m\u7873\'3fm m\u224\'e0 b\u7841\'3fn \u273\'3f\u227\'e3 mua (TurboCASH), bao g\u7891\'3fm b\u7845\'3ft k\u7923\'3f v\u237\'ed d\u7909\'3f v\u224\'e0 t\u224\'e0i li\u7879\'3fu n\u224\'e0o \u273\'3fi k\u232\'e8m. B\u7857\'3fng vi\u7879\'3fc nh\u7853\'3fp d\u7919\'3f li\u7879\'3fu ho\u7863\'3fc s\u7917\'3f d\u7909\'3fng c\u225\'e1c t\u7879\'3fp tin b\u7893\'3f tr\u7907\'3f/plugin, b\u7841\'3fn \u273\'3f\u7891\'3fng \u253\'fd ch\u7883\'3fu s\u7921\'3f r\u224\'e0ng bu\u7897\'3fc b\u7903\'3fi t\u7845\'3ft c\u7843\'3f c\u225\'e1c \u273\'3fi\u7873\'3fu kho\u7843\'3fn v\u224\'e0 \u273\'3fi\u7873\'3fu ki\u7879\'3fn c\u7911\'3fa th\u7887\'3fa thu\u7853\'3fn gi\u7845\'3fy ph\u233\'e9p n\u224\'e0y.}
{\lang2057\par}\pard\plain \s0\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\faauto\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang7177\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang7177\dbch\af8\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang7177\widctlpar\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\kerning0\f7\lang2057

{\lang2057\par}\pard\plain \s0\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\faauto\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang7177\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang7177\dbch\af8\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang7177\widctlpar\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\kerning0\f7\lang2057
Sau khi b\u7841\'3fn ch\u7845\'3fp nh\u7853\'3fn c\u225\'e1c \u273\'3fi\u7873\'3fu kho\u7843\'3fn v\u224\'e0 \u273\'3fi\u7873\'3fu ki\u7879\'3fn c\u7911\'3fa Th\u7887\'3fa thu\u7853\'3fn Gi\u7845\'3fy ph\u233\'e9p, b\u7841\'3fn \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc c\u7845\'3fp quy\u7873\'3fn s\u7917\'3f d\u7909\'3fng Ph\u7847\'3fn m\u7873\'3fm theo c\u225\'e1ch th\u7913\'3fc \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc quy \u273\'3f\u7883\'3fnh d\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fi \u273\'3f\u226\'e2y. Ph\u7847\'3fn m\u7873\'3fm n\u224\'e0y thu\u7897\'3fc s\u7903\'3f h\u7919\'3fu c\u7911\'3fa C\u225\'e1c Nh\u224\'e0 Cung C\u7845\'3fp v\u224\'e0 \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc b\u7843\'3fo v\u7879\'3f b\u7903\'3fi lu\u7853\'3ft b\u7843\'3fn quy\u7873\'3fn v\u224\'e0 c\u225\'e1c hi\u7879\'3fp \u432\'3f\u7899\'3fc b\u7843\'3fn quy\u7873\'3fn qu\u7889\'3fc t\u7871\'3f. Do \u273\'3f\u243\'f3, b\u7841\'3fn ph\u7843\'3fi \u273\'3f\u7889\'3fi x\u7917\'3f v\u7899\'3fi Ph\u7847\'3fn m\u7873\'3fm n\u224\'e0y nh\u432\'3f b\u7845\'3ft k\u7923\'3f t\u224\'e0i li\u7879\'3fu c\u243\'f3 b\u7843\'3fn quy\u7873\'3fn n\u224\'e0o kh\u225\'e1c. B\u7841\'3fn kh\u244\'f4ng \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc chuy\u7875\'3fn nh\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fng, cho thu\u234\'ea, cho m\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fn, s\u7917\'3fa \u273\'3f\u7893\'3fi, d\u7883\'3fch thu\u7853\'3ft, c\u7845\'3fp ph\u233\'e9p ph\u7909\'3f, chia s\u7867\'3f th\u7901\'3fi gian ho\u7863\'3fc truy\u7873\'3fn t\u7843\'3fi \u273\'3fi\u7879\'3fn t\u7917\'3f c\u225\'e1c kh\u243\'f3a c\u7845\'3fp ph\u233\'e9p ho\u7863\'3fc t\u224\'e0i li\u7879\'3fu.}
