B\u7841\'3fn kh\u244\'f4ng \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc b\u225\'e1n l\u7841\'3fi, cho thu\u234\'ea, ho\u7863\'3fc ph\u226\'e2n ph\u7889\'3fi ph\u7847\'3fn m\u7873\'3fm ho\u7863\'3fc s\u7889\'3f s\u234\'ea-ri m\u224\'e0 b\u7841\'3fn \u273\'3f\u227\'e3 nh\u7853\'3fn \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc. B\u7841\'3fn kh\u244\'f4ng \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc b\u225\'e1n l\u7841\'3fi, cho thu\u234\'ea ho\u7863\'3fc ph\u226\'e2n ph\u7889\'3fi c\u225\'e1c kh\u243\'f3a s\u234\'ea-ri d\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fi b\u7845\'3ft k\u7923\'3f h\u236\'ecnh th\u7913\'3fc n\u224\'e0o c\u7841\'3fnh tranh tr\u7921\'3fc ti\u7871\'3fp v\u7899\'3fi ng\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fi b\u225\'e1n. Vi\u7879\'3fc k\u7929\'3f thu\u7853\'3ft \u273\'3f\u7843\'3fo ng\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc, bi\u234\'ean d\u7883\'3fch ng\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc, ho\u7863\'3fc th\u225\'e1o r\u7901\'3fi Ph\u7847\'3fn m\u7873\'3fm b\u7883\'3f nghi\u234\'eam c\u7845\'3fm r\u245\'f5 r\u224\'e0ng.}
