{\kerning0\rtlch\ab\ltrch\hich\af7\alang2057\ab\dbch\ab\loch\f7\lang2057\b\par}\pard\plain \s0\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\faauto\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang7177\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang7177\dbch\af8\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang7177\widctlpar\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\kerning0\f7\lang2057
Ph\u7847\'3fn m\u7873\'3fm v\u224\'e0 t\u224\'e0i li\u7879\'3fu \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc cung c\u7845\'3fp tr\u234\'ean c\u417\'3f s\u7903\'3f \u8220\'93nguy\u234\'ean tr\u7841\'3fng\u8221\'94. M\u7885\'3fi r\u7911\'3fi ro thu\u7897\'3fc v\u7873\'3f b\u7841\'3fn. C\u225\'e1c Nh\u224\'e0 Cung C\u7845\'3fp kh\u244\'f4ng cam k\u7871\'3ft ho\u7863\'3fc b\u7843\'3fo \u273\'3f\u7843\'3fm r\u7857\'3fng ph\u7847\'3fn m\u7873\'3fm v\u224\'e0 t\u224\'e0i li\u7879\'3fu \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc cung c\u7845\'3fp kh\u244\'f4ng c\u243\'f3 l\u7895\'3fi ho\u7863\'3fc vi-r\u250\'fat, ho\u7863\'3fc ph\u7847\'3fn m\u7873\'3fm v\u224\'e0 t\u224\'e0i li\u7879\'3fu \u273\'3f\u243\'f3 ph\u249\'f9 h\u7907\'3fp cho m\u7909\'3fc \u273\'3f\u237\'edch s\u7917\'3f d\u7909\'3fng d\u7921\'3f \u273\'3f\u7883\'3fnh.}
