{\kerning0\rtlch\ab\ltrch\hich\af7\alang2057\ab\dbch\ab\loch\f7\lang2057\b\par}\pard\plain \s0\ql\nowidctlpar\hyphpar0\faauto\ltrpar\cf0\kerning1\rtlch\af11\afs24\alang7177\ltrch\hich\af3\afs24\alang7177\dbch\af8\langfe2052\loch\f3\fs24\lang7177\widctlpar\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0{\kerning0\f7\lang2057
Trong m\u7885\'3fi tr\u432\'3f\u7901\'3fng h\u7907\'3fp, C\u225\'e1c Nh\u224\'e0 Cung C\u7845\'3fp ho\u7863\'3fc c\u225\'e1c nh\u224\'e0 cung \u7913\'3fng c\u7911\'3fa h\u7885\'3f s\u7869\'3f kh\u244\'f4ng ch\u7883\'3fu tr\u225\'e1ch nhi\u7879\'3fm v\u7899\'3fi b\u7841\'3fn ho\u7863\'3fc b\u7845\'3ft k\u7923\'3f b\u234\'ean n\u224\'e0o kh\u225\'e1c v\u7873\'3f b\u7845\'3ft k\u7923\'3f thi\u7879\'3ft h\u7841\'3fi ng\u7851\'3fu nhi\u234\'ean, \u273\'3f\u7863\'3fc bi\u7879\'3ft ho\u7863\'3fc gi\u225\'e1n ti\u7871\'3fp, m\u7845\'3ft m\u225\'e1t d\u7919\'3f li\u7879\'3fu ho\u7863\'3fc d\u7919\'3f li\u7879\'3fu b\u7883\'3f tr\u7903\'3f n\u234\'ean kh\u244\'f4ng ch\u237\'ednh x\u225\'e1c, m\u7845\'3ft l\u7907\'3fi nhu\u7853\'3fn ho\u7863\'3fc doanh thu, ho\u7863\'3fc gi\u225\'e1n \u273\'3fo\u7841\'3fn kinh doanh d\u432\'3f\u7899\'3fi b\u7845\'3ft k\u7923\'3f h\u236\'ecnh th\u7913\'3fc n\u224\'e0o ph\u225\'e1t sinh t\u7915\'3f ho\u7863\'3fc li\u234\'ean quan \u273\'3f\u7871\'3fn vi\u7879\'3fc s\u7917\'3f d\u7909\'3fng ho\u7863\'3fc kh\u244\'f4ng th\u7875\'3f s\u7917\'3f d\u7909\'3fng ph\u7847\'3fn m\u7873\'3fm v\u224\'e0/ho\u7863\'3fc t\u224\'e0i li\u7879\'3fu, b\u7845\'3ft k\u7875\'3f h\u236\'ecnh th\u7913\'3fc h\u224\'e0nh \u273\'3f\u7897\'3fng n\u224\'e0o, cho d\u249\'f9 trong h\u7907\'3fp \u273\'3f\u7891\'3fng, sai ph\u7841\'3fm d\u226\'e2n s\u7921\'3f (bao g\u7891\'3fm c\u7843\'3f s\u417\'3f su\u7845\'3ft), tr\u225\'e1ch nhi\u7879\'3fm s\u7843\'3fn ph\u7849\'3fm nghi\u234\'eam ng\u7863\'3ft hay c\u225\'e1ch kh\u225\'e1c, ngay c\u7843\'3f khi b\u7845\'3ft k\u7923\'3f \u273\'3f\u7841\'3fi di\u7879\'3fn n\u224\'e0o c\u7911\'3fa C\u225\'e1c Nh\u224\'e0 Cung C\u7845\'3fp ho\u7863\'3fc nh\u224\'e0 cung \u7913\'3fng c\u7911\'3fa h\u7885\'3f \u273\'3f\u227\'e3 \u273\'3f\u432\'3f\u7907\'3fc th\u244\'f4ng b\u225\'e1o v\u7873\'3f kh\u7843\'3f n\u259\'3fng x\u7843\'3fy ra thi\u7879\'3ft h\u7841\'3fi nh\u432\'3f v\u7853\'3fy. S\u7921\'3f t\u7915\'3f ch\u7889\'3fi tr\u225\'e1ch nhi\u7879\'3fm \u273\'3f\u7889\'3fi v\u7899\'3fi c\u225\'e1c thi\u7879\'3ft h\u7841\'3fi n\u224\'e0y s\u7869\'3f kh\u244\'f4ng b\u7883\'3f \u7843\'3fnh h\u432\'3f\u7903\'3fng b\u7903\'3fi b\u7845\'3ft k\u7923\'3f s\u7921\'3f th\u7845\'3ft b\u7841\'3fi n\u224\'e0o.}
